ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act (Maanulth First Nations)
PrecisOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT (MAANULTH FIRST NATIONS) in order to enable each of the five Maanulth First Nations, with agreement of the Government of Canada, to implement a First Nations Goods and Services Tax within their lands.
